Package org.acumos.federation.gateway

Class DockerConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.acumos.federation.gateway.DockerConfig
  • public class DockerConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    Configuration bean for Docker access parameters. These parameters are passed verbatim to withXXX() methods of the DefaultDockerClientConfig.Builder class.
